                                <p>By giving your email address, we can assign your inquiry and answer you. Your personal data will not be given to any third parties when using the contact form.</p>
                                <p>b. Legal basis<br>The processing of personal data for contact purposes (cf. § 4 5. a.) takes place according to Article 6 para. 1 lit. a GDPR based on the voluntary declaration of consent that you provide:</p>
